'''Alexander Hatrick''' (29 August 1857 &ndash; 30 July 1918) was a New Zealand merchant, shipowner, tourism entrepreneur and mayor. He was born in [[Smythesdale]], [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]], [[Australia]] on 29 August 1857.<ref name="DNZB Hatrick">{{DNZB|title=Alexander Hatrick|first= Diana|last= Beaglehole|id=2h20|accessdate=5 February 2012}}</ref>

