[https://www.facebook.com/eliezer.souza Eliézer de Souza] is a brazilian entrepreneur, producer and publisher based in [[São Paulo]], [[Brazil]].

He has collaborated with a variety of projects in the entertainment and media businesses such as [http://propmark.com.br/midia/dj-mag-chega-ao-brasil DJ Mag Brasil], [http://www.pacha.com/pachamagazine/index.php?id=62 Pacha Ibiza Magazine], [http://www.industriae.com.br/ Pacha Brasil Newspaper], [https://www.flickr.com/photos/curvas/2588508497/in/album-72157604881691911/ Sirena Magazine], [http://gooutside.com.br/ Go Outside Brasil] ([http://www.editora3.com.br/ Editora Três] / [http://rockymountain.com.br/ Rocky Mountain]), [https://www.flickr.com/photos/curvas/albums/72157604860443588 Curvas Beachwear], [https://www.flickr.com/photos/curvas/2578033509/in/album-72157604881691911/ Revista Academia Esportes] ([http://agenciasmart.com.br/ Agência Smart]), [http://revistasdjsedancemusicabrasil.blogspot.com.br/2013/03/revista-planet-pop-no-6-2004.html Planet Pop Magazine] ([http://www.buildingrecords.com.br/ Building Records]), [http://saxmagazine.com/ S.A.X. Magazine], [http://www.djguide.com.br/ DJ Guide] and many others.

Since 2008, actively working on the development of [http://mixmag.com.br/ Mixmag Brazil], helping to grow the world's largest dance music media brand's in the biggest country of South America.

