{{Infobox officeholder |name = Patrick Bernasconi |image = Patrick_Bernasconi.jpg |office = [[French Economic, Social and Environmental Council|President of the French Economic, Social and Environmental Council]] |president = [[François Hollande]] |term_start = 1 December 2015 |term_end = |predecessor = [[Jean-Paul Delevoye]] |successor = |office1 = President of the Fédération nationale des travaux publics |term_start1 = 2005 |term_end1 = 17 September 2013 |constituency1 = |predecessor1 = |successor1 = |office2 = |term_start2 = |term_end2 = |predecessor2 = |successor2 = |birth_date = {{birth date and age|1955|7|16|df=y}} |birth_place = [[Domjean]], [[Fance]] |death_date = |death_place = |party = |spouse = |alma_mater = [[École Spéciale des Travaux Publics]] }} '''Patrick Bernasconi''' (born 16 July 1955 in [[Domjean]]) is a [[France|French]] [[business executive]]. He is responsible for four public works companies. He was elected president of the [[French Economic, Social and Environmental Council]] on 1 December 2015.<ref>{{cite web|title=Un entrepreneur, Patrick Bernasconi, à la tête du Cese|url=http://lentreprise.lexpress.fr/actualites/1/actualites/un-entrepreneur-patrick-bernasconi-a-la-tete-du-cese_1741442.html|website=l'express|accessdate=18 April 2016|language=fr}}</ref>
A graduate of the [[École Spéciale des Travaux Publics]], he was the president of the National Federation of Public Works (FNTP) from 2005 to 2013<ref>{{cite web|title=Bruno Cavagné succède à Patrick Bernasconi à la tête de la FNTP|url=http://www.lepoint.fr/bourse/bruno-cavagne-succede-a-patrick-bernasconi-a-la-tete-de-la-fntp-19-09-2013-1733017_81.php|website=lepoint.fr|accessdate=18 April 2016}}</ref> and executive board member of the [[MEDEF]].
== Biography == As his surname suggests, Bernasconi is the grandson of an Italian bricklayer immigrant from [[Trentino]] ([[Molina di Ledro]]) who emigrated to [[Normandy]] in 1920.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Oriot|first1=Xavier|title=Patrick Bernasconi, de Domjean au patronat à Paris|url=http://www.entreprises.ouest-france.fr/article/patrick-bernasconi-domjean-au-patronat-paris-03-02-2013-84196|publisher=Ouest-France|accessdate=18 April 2016}}</ref>
